# Project Overview

This is a full-stack Bulk Email Campaign Manager application, structured as a monorepo.

-   `BulkEmailCampaignManager/backend/`: Contains the Node.js/Express backend server. See [backend-architecture.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/backend-architecture.mdc) for details.
-   `BulkEmailCampaignManager/frontend/`: Contains the React (Vite) frontend application. See [frontend-architecture.mdc](mdc:.cursor/rules/frontend-architecture.mdc) for details.
-   `BulkEmailCampaignManager/README.md`: [Project README](mdc:BulkEmailCampaignManager/README.md) with setup instructions and features.

The application allows users to create, manage, and track bulk email campaigns with real-time analytics.

